<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.15;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;font-size: 14px;height: 100%;">
    <title>Pillars</title> 
    <head>
      <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/2.2.13/semantic.min.css">
      <style>
          #grey { 
              background-color: LightGrey;
          }
      </style>   
    </head>
    <body style="margin: 0;padding: 0;overflow-x: hidden;min-width: 320px;background: #fff;font-family: Lato,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.4285em;color: rgba(0,0,0,.87);font-smoothing: antialiased;height: 100%;">

        <div class="ui segment" id="grey" style="position: relative;background: #fff;box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.15);margin: 1rem 0;padding: 1em 1em;border-radius: .28571429rem;border: 1px solid rgba(34,36,38,.15);font-size: 1rem;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;background-color: LightGrey;">
            <img class="ui centered tiny image" src="https://pillars.school/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/cropped-pillars-logo2.png" height="80" width="80" style="border-style: none;position: relative;display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;background-color: transparent;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;width: 80px;height: auto;font-size: .85714286rem;">
            <div class="ui segment" style="position: relative;background: #fff;box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.15);margin: 1rem 0;padding: 1em 1em;border-radius: .28571429rem;border: 1px solid rgba(34,36,38,.15);font-size: 1rem;margin-bottom: 0;">
                <h3 class="ui header" style="font-family: Lato,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;line-height: 1.28571429em;margin: calc(2rem - .14285714em) 0 1rem;font-weight: 700;padding: 0 0;font-size: 1.28571429rem;margin-top: -.14285714em;border: none;text-transform: none;color: rgba(0,0,0,.87);">
                    Welkom bij Pillars, <%=firstName%> <%=lastName%>
                </h3>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;margin-top: 0;">De directie van jouw school heeft je uitgenodigd om deel te nemen aan Pillars.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">Je kunt inloggen op de <a href="https://pillars.school" style="background-color: transparent;-webkit-text-decoration-skip: objects;color: #4183c4;text-decoration: none;">Pillars website</a> met:</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">Gebruikersnaam: <strong style="font-weight: bolder;"><%=username%></strong></p>
                <%if(firstName){%>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">Wachtwoord: <strong style="font-weight: bolder;"><%=password%></strong></p>
                <%} else {%>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">Jouw admin heeft een account voor je gemaakt met het school account.</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">Gebruik de knoppen voor Office365 of Google for Education om in te loggen.</p>
                <% } %>
                <a class="fluid ui green button" href="https://app.pillars.school/login" style="background-color: #21ba45;-webkit-text-decoration-skip: objects;color: #fff;text-decoration: none;cursor: pointer;display: block;min-height: 1em;outline: 0;border: none;vertical-align: baseline;background: #e0e1e2 none;font-family: Lato,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;margin: 0 .25em 0 0;padding: .78571429em 1.5em .78571429em;text-transform: none;text-shadow: none;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1em;font-style: normal;text-align: center;border-radius: .28571429rem;box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(34,36,38,.15) inset;-webkit-user-select: none;-moz-user-select: none;-ms-user-select: none;user-select: none;-webkit-transition: opacity .1s ease,background-color .1s ease,color .1s ease,box-shadow .1s ease,background .1s ease;transition: opacity .1s ease,background-color .1s ease,color .1s ease,box-shadow .1s ease,background .1s ease;will-change: '';-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 1rem;width: 100%;background-image: none;">Klik Hier Om Nu In Te Loggen!</a>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">We wensen je veel succes met het gebruik van Pillars.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;">Met vriendelijke groeten, </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 1em;line-height: 1.4285em;margin-bottom: 0;"><strong style="font-weight: bolder;">Team Pillars</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>    